verses.verse: Rejoice <S%H7442><s%> in Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, O ye righteous <S%H6662><s%>: Praise <S%H8416><s%> is comely <S%H5000><s%> for the upright <S%H6662><s%>.
Give thanks <S%H3034><s%> unto Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> with the harp <S%H3658><s%>: Sing <S%H2167><s%> praises unto him with the psaltery <S%H5035><s%> of ten strings <S%H6218><s%>.
Sing <S%H7891><s%> unto him a new <S%H2319><s%> song <S%H7892><s%>; Play <S%H5059><s%> skilfully <S%H3190><s%> with a loud noise <S%H8643><s%>.
For the word <S%H1697><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> is right <S%H3477><s%>; And all his work <S%H4639><s%> is done in faithfulness <S%H530><s%>.
He loveth <S%H157><s%> righteousness <S%H6666><s%> and justice <S%H4941><s%>: The earth <S%H776><s%> is full <S%H4390><s%> of the lovingkindness <S%H2617><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>.
By the word <S%H1697><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> were the heavens <S%H8064><s%> made <S%H6213><s%>, And all the host <S%H6635><s%> of them by the breath <S%H7307><s%> of his mouth <S%H6310><s%>.
He gathereth <S%H3664><s%> the waters <S%H4325><s%> of the sea <S%H3220><s%> together as a heap <S%H5067><s%>: He layeth up <S%H5414><s%> the deeps <S%H8415><s%> in store-houses <S%H214><s%>.
Let all the earth <S%H776><s%> fear <S%H3372><s%> Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>: Let all the inhabitants <S%H3427><s%> of the world <S%H8398><s%> stand in awe of him <S%H1481><s%>.
For he spake <S%H559><s%>, and it was done <S%H6680><s%>; He commanded, and it stood fast <S%H5975><s%>.

Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> bringeth <S%H6331><s%> the counsel <S%H6098><s%> of the nations <S%H1471><s%> to nought <S%H6331><s%>; He maketh <S%H5106><s%> the thoughts <S%H4284><s%> of the peoples <S%H5971><s%> to be of no effect <S%H5106><s%>.

The counsel <S%H6098><s%> of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> standeth <S%H5975><s%> fast for ever <S%H5769><s%>, The thoughts <S%H4284><s%> of his heart <S%H3820><s%> to all <S%H1755><s%> generations <S%H1755><s%>.
Blessed <S%H835><s%> is the nation <S%H1471><s%> whose God <S%H430><s%> is Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, The people <S%H5971><s%> whom he hath chosen <S%H977><s%> for his own inheritance <S%H5159><s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> looketh <S%H5027><s%> from heaven <S%H8064><s%>; He beholdeth <S%H7200><s%> all the sons <S%H1121><s%> of men <S%H120><s%>;
From the place <S%H4349><s%> of his habitation <S%H3427><s%> he looketh <S%H7688><s%> forth Upon all the inhabitants <S%H3427><s%> of the earth <S%H776><s%>,
He that fashioneth <S%H3335><s%> the hearts <S%H3820><s%> of them all <S%H3162><s%>, That considereth <S%H995><s%> all their works <S%H4639><s%>.

There is no king <S%H4428><s%> saved <S%H3467><s%> by the multitude <S%H7230><s%> of a host <S%H2428><s%>: A mighty man <S%H1368><s%> is not delivered <S%H5337><s%> by great <S%H7230><s%> strength <S%H3581><s%>.
A horse <S%H5483><s%> is a vain thing <S%H8267><s%> for safety <S%H8668><s%>; Neither doth he deliver <S%H4422><s%> any by his great <S%H7230><s%> power <S%H2428><s%>.
Behold <S%H5869><s%>, the eye of Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> is upon them that fear <S%H3373><s%> him <S%H3176><s%>, Upon them that hope in his lovingkindness <S%H2617><s%>;
To deliver <S%H5337><s%> their soul <S%H5315><s%> from death <S%H4194><s%>, And to keep them alive <S%H2421><s%> in famine <S%H7458><s%>.
Our soul <S%H5315><s%> hath waited <S%H2442><s%> for Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>: He is our help <S%H5828><s%> and our shield <S%H4043><s%>.
For our heart <S%H3820><s%> shall rejoice <S%H8055><s%> in him <S%H982><s%>, Because we have trusted in his holy <S%H6944><s%> name <S%H8034><s%>.
Let thy lovingkindness <S%H2617><s%>, O Jehovah <S%H3068><s%>, be upon us <S%H3176><s%>, According as we have hoped in thee.
